GIAN Course on Turbulence modelling 

Body:
b'        Dear all,      As part of the GIAN program ),  a one week course on Turbulence modelling will be conducted at IIT Madras.       Title of the course:  Turbulence modeling for Engineering Application   Faculty : Professor Paul Durbin, Department of Aerospace Engineering, IOWA state University, USA.    Duration: May 17  May 23, .    Last Date for Registration through GIAN website: March 31, 2016      Participant shortlisting and intimation: April 15, 2016      Students of IIT Madras selected to attend this course cancredit it as a 1credit (in the old credit system) course.             Professor Paul Durbin is a developer of the famous v2f model.It is a wonderful opportunity to listen to him on this important topic.           With warm regards,  S.Vengadesan, Department of Applied Mechanics, IIT Madras, Chennai  36, India     '

